(40, 'Our company', 'company-en-gb', '<p>CHITOS S.A. is one of the most pioneer and successful Greek companies, with a leading presence to the area of bottled water. Having a registered office at the region of Ioannina and along with an experience at the sector of soft drink’s bottling already from 1955, has started with the bottling of Natural Mineral Water “ZAGORI” at 1988. It has been evolved steadily into a dynamically developing Company, which contributes continuously and essentially to the national economy.</p>\r\n<p>The firm commitment of CHITOS S.A. to the principles of total quality as far as the produced product is concerned, allows it to support with responsibility the fact that every drop of the Natural Mineral Water “ZAGORI” preserves unchanging the nature of Epirus. </p>\r\n<p>Today, CHITOS S.A. has two privately owned recognized springs of natural mineral water and two bottling plants, with eight production lines to the regions of Perivleptos and Kranoula of the broader region of Zagorochoria. At the same time, it has a third industrial plant to the Industrial Zone (VI.PE.) of Ioannina, in which are manufactured pet – preforms and plastic caps through vertical integration and supporting of the two fillers operation.</p>\r\n<p>CHITOS S.A. emerges as the most recognizable and competitive company to the sector of bottled natural mineral waters with the biggest range of packaging and services, employing directly and indirectly more than 1.200 persons in total.</p>\r\n<p>The bottling of the Natural Mineral Water “ZAGORI” is carried out to the spring, by using sophisticated machinery, without any human intervention during the whole procedure from the pumping, up to the disposal of the product and without coming between any treatment.</p>\r\n<p>The manufacture of the product is carried out under the most strict quality specifications and in full compliance with the European and national legislation.</p>\r\n<p>CHITOS S.A., having as a target to ensure its commitment towards its consumers in order to provide products and services of high and consistent quality, applies:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Quality Management System, according to the standard ISO 9001 (from 2003)</li>\r\n<li>Food Safety Management System according to the standard ISO 22000 (from 2009)</li>\r\n<li>Current Rules of Good Industrial and Hygiene Practice. CHITOS S.A., is the only Greek Company which has the compliance certificate in force in accordance with the requirements of the code of hygiene practice WE (Watercoolers Europe - ex EBWA)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>The application of the above systems is certified by international certification bodies such as TUV HELLAS and NSF International which control the proper application-compliance and the continuous upgrading of the quality systems with annual inspections.</p>\r\n<p> </p>', 27, 0, 1, 1, 1, '40.jpg', '{"inheritFrom":"0","catMetaDesc":"","catMetaKey":"","catMetaRobots":"","catMetaAuthor":"","theme":"category-company","num_leading_items":"200","num_leading_columns":"1","leadingImgSize":"Large","num_primary_items":"4","num_primary_columns":"2","primaryImgSize":"Medium","num_secondary_items":"4","num_secondary_columns":"1","secondaryImgSize":"Small","num_links":"4","num_links_columns":"1","linksImgSize":"XSmall","catCatalogMode":"0","catFeaturedItems":"1","catOrdering":"order","catPagination":"2","catPaginationResults":"1","catTitle":"1","catTitleItemCounter":"1","catDescription":"1","catImage":"1","catFeedLink":"1","catFeedIcon":"1","subCategories":"1","subCatColumns":"2","subCatOrdering":"","subCatTitle":"1","subCatTitleItemCounter":"1","subCatDescription":"1","subCatImage":"1","itemImageXS":"","itemImageS":"","itemImageM":"","itemImageL":"","itemImageXL":"","catItemTitle":"1","catItemTitleLinked":"1","catItemFeaturedNotice":"0","catItemAuthor":"0","catItemDateCreated":"0","catItemRating":"0","catItemImage":"1","catItemIntroText":"1","catItemIntroTextWordLimit":"","catItemExtraFields":"0","catIt