(58, 'Environmental awareness', 'enviromental-en', '<div class="itemFullText">\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">With respect to the environment</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Everybody in CHITOS S.A. consider as their duty to offer to the consumers the most precious commodity of nature, water, in excellent quality, as exactly it runs from its springs.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Based on this principle, is followed a new standard of qualitative operation, friendly towards the environment and the consumers, with emphasis on the green development, the sustainability and the innovation. Thus, from 2003 the company participates actively to the Recycling programs, while from 2010 constitutes a member of the National Collection System “Reciprocal Recycling”.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">In fact, by implementing the innovation, CHITOS S.A constitutes the unique Greek company which has been contracted with Deutsche Pfandsystem GmbH for the recycling of the packages in Germany. In particular, its products which are exported to Germany bear the sign of the recycling system “DPG”, having as a result the packages to be “recognized” easily by the automatic machines of recycling.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">With respect to the environment, CHITOS S.A has proceed also to the abolition of freon usage at air conditioning systems and cooling circuits, while from 2005 it invests to the usage of energy saving systems to its plants.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"> </p>\r\n</div>', 32, 0, 1, 1, 2, '58.jpg', '{"inheritFrom":"8","catMetaDesc":"","catMetaKey":"","catMetaRobots":"","catMetaAuthor":"","theme":"subcategory-news","num_leading_items":"2","num_leading_columns":"1","leadingImgSize":"Large","num_primary_items":"4","num_primary_columns":"2","primaryImgSize":"Medium","num_secondary_items":"4","num_secondary_columns":"1","secondaryImgSize":"Small","num_links":"4","num_links_columns":"1","linksImgSize":"XSmall","catCatalogMode":"0","cat