(89, 'History', 'history-en', 40, 1, '<p><span style="display: none;">Starting his business activity in the mid ’50s with the foundation of the bottling factory of sparkling drinks to the city of Ioannina– capable to support with pretensions the market of the prefecture and the regions around–, Ioannis Chitos, who comes from Asprochori at Souli of Ioannina will have to wait something less than three and a half decades in order to see the shaping of the bright future of its soft drinks plant which was initially small in size.</span></p>\r\n<p><strong>1955</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong><img class="img-responsive" title="1955" src="images/history_1955.jpg" alt="1955" /></strong></p>\r\n<p>Starting his business activity in the mid ’50s with the foundation of the bottling factory of sparkling drinks to the city of Ioannina– capable to support with pretensions the market of the prefecture and the regions around–, Ioannis Chitos, who comes from Asprochori at Souli of Ioannina will have to wait something less than three and a half decades in order to see the shaping of the bright future of its soft drinks plant which was initially small in size.</p>\r\n<p>With the help of his two sons, Konstantinos and Alcibiades, the first efforts of the business will be the manufacture of the soft drinks “Ermis”.</p>\r\n<p><strong>1980</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong><img class="img-responsive" title="1980" src="images/history_1980.jpg" alt="1980" /></strong></p>\r\n<p>In 1980, when Ioannis Chitos is withdrawn from the effective administration of the business, his sons change its name to “High Juice”. This is also the first move of Chitos brothers in marketing.</p>\r\n<p><strong>1984</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong><img class="img-responsive" title="1984" src="images/history_1984.jpg" alt="1984" /></strong></p>\r\n<p>In 1984 Chitos brothers sign an agreement with Coca-Cola 3E and start bottling on behalf of it the soft drinks of wide circulation, while they stop manufacturing their own. At the same time they “conceive” and process a new business plan which in spite of the risk that seems to have, due to the consumption habits of the period, during its course in the future will be established with the insistence and the diligence demonstrated by both of the brothers.</p>\r\n<p><strong>1988</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong><img class="img-responsive" title="1988" src="images/history_1988.jpg" alt="1988" /></strong></p>\r\n<p>A little before the ’90s, the future of the Company is signaled again, with the important decision to change the course of the business and to implement the plan for its introduction into the domestic market of the bottled water with its own brand. In a period during which the consumption of the bottled water is still quite low in Greece, CHITOS S.A. dares, along with its “main vehicle” which is the know how and the experience of 30 and more years to the market of the soft drinks and a Spring of Natural Mineral Water, which derives from a pristine area of an endless natural beauty, Zagori.</p>\r\n<p><strong>1992</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong><img class="img-responsive" title="1992" src="images/history_1992.jpg" alt="1992" /></strong></p>\r\n<p>Commencement of the second plant of water bottling “ZAGORI” to the same region by the second spring that is disposed by CHITOS.</p>\r\n<p><strong>1995</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong><img class="img-responsive" title="1995" src="images/history_1995.jpg" alt="1995" /></strong></p>\r\n<p>Recognition of the springs of the Company as springs of Natural Mineral Water “ZAGORI” (Identification number: Y2/. 3716/18.12.95, according to our records).</p>\r\n<p><strong>2002</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong><img class="img-responsive" title="2002" src="images/history_2002.jpg" alt="2002" /></strong></p>\r\n<p>Recognition of the springs of the Company as springs of Natural Mineral Water “ZAGORI” (Identification number: Y2/ 3716/18.12.95, according to our records).</p>\r\n<p><strong>2006</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong><img class="img-responsive" title="2006" src="images/history_2006.jpg" alt="2006" /></strong></p>\r\n<p>Recognition of the springs of the Company as springs of Natural Mineral Water “ZAGORI” (Identification number: Y2/3716/18.12.95, according to our records).</p>\r\n<p><strong>Today</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong><img class="img-responsive" title="Today" src="images/history_today.jpg" alt="Today" /></strong></p>\r\n<p>Today CHITOS S.A. is one of the most pioneer and successful Greek companies with leading presence to the sector of bottled waters, which contributes continuously and essentially to the national economy.</p>\r\n<p>It has two privately owned recognized springs of natural mineral water and two plants of bottling, with eight production lines to the regions of Perivleptos and Kranoula of the broader region of Zagorohoria. At the same time, it has a third industrial plant to the Industrial Zone (VI.PE.) of Ioannina, in which are manufactured pet – preforms and plastic caps through vertical integration and supporting of the two fillers operation.</p>\r\n<p>CHITOS S.A. emerges as the most recognizable and competitive company to the sector of bottled natural mineral waters, with the biggest range of packaging and services, employing directly and indirectly more than 1.200 persons in total.</p>\r\n<p><b> </b></p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p><b> </b></p>', '', NULL, NULL, '[]', '', '2016-11-25 13:26:13', 191, '', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2016-11-25 14:25:06', 191, '2016-11-01 14:22:51', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1, 1, 0, 0, '', '', '', '', 6, '{"catItemTitle":"","catItemTitleLinked":"","catItemFeaturedNotice":"","catItemAuthor":"","catItemDateCreated":"","catItemRating":"","catItemImage":"","catItemIntroText":"","catItemExtraFields":"","catItemHits":"","catItemCategory":"","catItemTags":"","catItemAttachments":"","catItemAttachmentsCounter":"","catItemVideo":"","catItemVideoWidth":"","catItemVideoHeight":"","catItemAudioWidth":"","catItemAudioHeight":"","catItemVideoAutoPlay":"","catItemImageGalle