(90, 'Administration - vision', 'vision-en', 40, 1, '<p>CHITOS S.A. constitutes a characteristic example of a healthy Greek business, which is adapted to the signs of the particular period and follows the development, having a powerful administration team which is characterized by harmony of decisions and mainly mood for work.</p>\r\n<p>The management team of the business is composed of three, dynamic personalities with increased competences and high duties:</p>\r\n<p>Nikos Chitos, Chairman of the Board of Directors of CHITOS S.A.</p>\r\n<p>Vasilis Chitos, Vice President of the Board of Directors of CHITOS S.A.</p>\r\n<p>Ioannis Chitos, Vice President of the Board of Directors of CHITOS S.A.</p>\r\n<p>All together, and each one separately, compose the successful formula, which through the passage of time is adapted by CHITOS S.A., to the healthy “business”. Through responsible operation, all those years, the leading team of CHITOS envisages the future and invests to the development with the style of “ZAGORI”.</p>\r\n<p> </p>', '', NULL, NULL, '[]', '', '2016-11-25 13:26:13', 191, '', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2016-11-25 13:34:46', 191, '2016-11-01 14:22:51', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1, 2, 0, 0, '', '', '', '', 0, '{"catItemTitle":"","catItemTitleLinked":"","catItemFeaturedNotice":"","catItemAuthor":"","catItemDateCreated":"","catItemRating":"","catItemImage":"","catItemIntroText":"","catItemExtraFields":"","catItemHits":"","catItemCategory":"","catItemTags":"","catItemAttachments":"","catItemAttachmentsCounter":"","catItemVideo":"","catItemVideoWidth":"","catItemVideoHeight":"","catItemAudioWidth":"","catItemAudioHeight":"","catItemVideoAutoPlay":"","catItemImageGallery":"","catItemImageGalleryWidth":"","catItemImageGalleryHeight":"","catItemDateModified":"","catItemReadMore":"","catItemCommentsAnchor":"","catItemK2Plugins":"","itemDateCreated":"","itemTitle":"","itemFeaturedNotice":"","itemAuthor":"","itemFontResizer":"","itemPrintButton":"","itemEmailButton":"",