(92, 'Distinctions', 'distinctions-en', 40, 1, '<p>CHITOS S.A. has received many and important distinctions until today, regarding its philosophy, its social work, its offer to the local community as well as its business ethics and the continuous support of the country’s economy. The Natural Mineral Water ZAGORI has received respective awarding for the communication, its position in the market, its modern packaging and its offer to the consumers.</p>\r\n<p>The distinctions came gradually to the history of CHITOS S.A. in order to confirm and set off the successful course of the company. However, the greatest achievement of the company is that it manages for 29 years to hold a special place to the hearts of the consumers, offering them the qualitative Natural Mineral Water ZAGORI.</p>\r\n<p>The most important awards, received by the company starting from the most recent, as follow:</p>\r\n<p><strong>2016</strong>: For 5th consecutive year CHITOS SA receives the Award “Diamonds - The Most Admired Enterprises 2016”.</p>\r\n<p><strong>2016</strong>:  Ermis Awards, Audience Award for the film “The Flight” from the Campaign “ZAGORI, good is within”</p>\r\n<p><strong>2016</strong>: Ermis Silver Award in the category Social Corporate Responsibility / Sponsorship / Culture / Education / Sports for the campaign “ZAGORI, good is within”.</p>\r\n<p><strong>2015</strong>: CHITOS SA was distinguished for its export performance with the award “Active Business Awards 2015”.</p>\r\n<p><strong>2015</strong>: For 4th consecutive year CHITOS SA receives the Award “Diamonds - The Most Admired Enterprises 2016”.</p>\r\n<p><strong>2015</strong>: CHITOS SA was distinguished for 2nd time as one of the “True Leaders” of the Greek Economy, in the frame of the ICAP Group event, which rewards Companies and Groups that constitute Leaders, based on four measurable criteria on published results..</p>\r\n<p><strong>2015</strong>: The sponsorship made by ZAGORI in cooperation with the North Face and the Fifth Element, entitled "North Face Zagori Mountain Running", received the Silver Award at the Tourism Awards 2015.</p>\r\n<p><strong>2015</strong>:  The TV spot campaign "ZAGORI, good is within” has excelled at the international Festivals of the 22nd Golden Drum.</p>\r\n<p><strong>2015</strong>:  The TV spot campaign "ZAGORI, good is within” has received the Silver Award to the International Festival of Creativity “Epica Awards 2015”.</p>\r\n<p><strong>2015</strong>:  The Federation of Industries of Northern Greece (FING) awarded CHITOS SA for its Corporate Social Responsibility.</p>\r\n<p><strong>2015</strong>: Natural mineral water ZAGORI excelled at the TOP BRANDS 2015 event by receiving the first place among bottled natural mineral water brands, based on IRI sales data for wide consumer products sold in supermarket chains.</p>\r\n<p><strong>2014</strong>: For 3rd consecutive year CHITOS SA receives the Award “Diamonds - The Most Admired Enterprises 2016”.</p>\r\n<p><strong>2014</strong>: CHITOS SA was distinguished as one of the “True Leaders” of the Greek Economy, in the frame of the ICAP Group event, which rewards Companies and Groups that constitute Leaders, based on four measurable criteria on published results..</p>\r\n<p><strong>2014</strong>: Federation of Industries of Northern Greece (FING) awarded CHITOS SA with a significant ward "Excellence- Medium Enterprise” for its steady growth, innovative entrepreneurship, investing in extraversion and social work, both locally and in the wider environment.</p>\r\n<p><strong>2014</strong>: Natural mineral water ZAGORI excelled at the TOP BRANDS 2015 event by receiving the first place among bottled natural mineral water brands, based on IRI sales data for wide consumer products sold in supermarket chains.</p>\r\n<p><strong>2014</strong>: The official site of the natural mineral water “ZAGORI” in Facebook received the Gold Award at the Social Media Awards competition.</p>\r\n<p><strong>2014</strong>: The TV spot with subject “Swamp it my ΖΑΓΟΡΙ” received the Bronze medal, in at the Award for 2014.</p>\r\n<p><strong>2013</strong>: For 3rd consecutive year the company CHITOS S.A. receives the distinction “Diamonds - The Most Admired Enterprises 2012”.</p>\r\n<p><strong>2012</strong>: For 2nd consecutive year the company CHITOS S.A. receives the distinction “Diamonds - The Most Admired Enterprises 2012”.</p>\r\n<p>The selection was made between the 3.500 larger businesses of the country, based on 10 financial indexes, which are defined as certification criteria of the credibility and their healthy course.</p>\r\n<p><strong>2011</strong>: Distinction «Diamonds - The Most Admired Enterprises of 2011». The company CHITOS S.A. was included into the healthiest developing industrial businesses during the period of crisis, which are presented to the annual Business Guide «Diamonds 2011» of STAT BANK.</p>\r\n<p><strong>2011</strong>: CHITOS S.A. was integrated again to the «STRONGEST COMPANIES IN GREECE» of ICAP Group.</p>\r\n<p>The “Strongest Companies in Greece” are the businesses which are classified to the most powerful zones of credit ratings of ICAP Group. ICAP Group is recognized by the Bank of Greece as an External Organisation of Credit Assessments as well as by the European Central Bank as Acceptable Source of Credit Assessments. Only one from ten businesses in Greece has the ability to be integrated into the community “Strongest Companies in Greece”.</p>\r\n<p><strong>2010</strong>: CHITOS S.A. was integrated into the «STRONGEST COMPANIES IN GREECE» of ICAP Group, as one of the most powerful companies in Greece, ready to face the challenges of the particular period, by confirming that its creditworthiness is really high. </p>\r\n<p><strong>2008</strong>: For 3rd year the First Award at FAMOUS BRANDS, to the category “Bottled Water ”.</p>\r\n<p><strong>2009</strong>: The advertising campaign with title “Heroes” was found to the list of finalist of the international competition EACA Care Awards, where companies are participating all over the world, based on their social contribution.</p>\r\n<p><strong>2009</strong>: Silver award to Ermis Awards for the advertising spot «HEROES»</p>\r\n<p><strong>2009</strong>: ACCOLADE for CHITOS S.A., from the Center of Special Vocational Education for its kind offer to the difficult work of the body.</p>\r\n<p><strong>2008</strong>: For 2nd year the First award at FAMOUS BRANDS, to the category “Bottled Water”.</p>\r\n<p><strong>2008</strong>: Second award to EFFIE AWARDS for the advertising campaign of the mineral water “ZAGORI”, with title “Provision of bottled water to the region Giousigkou of Kenya”.</p>\r\n<p><strong>2008</strong>: The television campaign of the company with title “In Kenya they are thirsty” was voted as the “Campaign of the Year” to www.epikoinoniakoi.blogspot.gr.</p>\r\n<p><strong>2008</strong>: CHITOS S.A. was ranked fifth to the social barometer A.S.B.I., according to which the citizens recognize the socially responsible companies which stood out in the sector of the Corporate Social Responsibility.</p>\r\n<p><strong>2007</strong>: Silver award to Ermis Awards  for the film with title “THIRST”</p>\r\n<p><strong>2007</strong>: First award to FAMOUS BRANDS, to the category “Bottled Water”.</p>\r\n<p><strong>2006</strong>: Silver award to EFFIE AWARDS for the advertising campaign of the mineral water "ZAGORI", with title “Zagorakis”.</p>\r\n<p><strong>2005</strong>: Distinction of the packaging PET 1lt, to the international competition “Βottlewaterworld design awards”.</p>\r\n<p><strong>2004</strong>: The natural mineral water ZAGORI was distinguished as one of the top 10 products which stood out to the sector of Foods and Drinks.</p>', '', NULL, NULL, '[]', '', '2016-11-25 13:26:13', 191, '', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2016-11-25 13:43:15', 191, '2016-11-01 14:22:51', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1, 4, 0, 0, '', '', '', '', 1, '{"catItemTitle":"","catItemTitleLinked":"","catIt