(104, 'The springs', 'springs-en', 29, 1, '<p>CHITOS S.A. has two privately owned recognized springs of natural mineral water to the feet of the massif Mitsikeli – Zagorochoria.       </p>\r\n<p>The aquafer, from which is taken “ZAGORI” water – proven by special hydrogeological studies and analyses – is protected against any external influence and pollution of the environment, while its physical construction ensures the consistent quality. The geological formations of the region give the particular content of the water to metals and nonmetal elements, by shaping thus its balanced taste, while they serve also as natural filters during its path towards the underground aquiferous basin where it is concentrated throughout the year, and gets rid of the presence of pathogenic microorganisms.</p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p><img title="Η διαδρομή του νερού" src="images/diagramma.jpg" alt="Η διαδρομή του νερού" width="600" height="374" /></p>', '', NULL, NULL, '[]', '', '2016-11-25 15:51:31', 191, '', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2016-11-25 15:52:55', 191, '2016-11-17 14:29:10', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1, 1, 0, 0, '', '', '', '', 1, '{"catItemTitle":"","catItemTitleLinked":"","catItemFeaturedNotice":"","catItemAuthor":"","catItemDateCreated":"","catItemRating":"","catItemImage":"","catItemIntroText":"","catItemExtraFields":"","catItemHits":"","catItemCategory":"","catItemTags":"","catItemAttachments":"","catItemAttachmentsCounter":"","catItemVideo":"","catItemVideoWidth":"","catItemVideoHeight":"","catItemAudioWidth":"","catItemAudioHeight":"","catItemVideoAutoPlay":"","catItemImageGallery":"","catItemImageGalleryWidth":"","catItemImageGalleryHeight":"","catItemDateModified":"","catItemReadMore":"","catItemCommentsAnchor":"","catItemK2Plugins":"","itemDateCreated":"","itemTitle":"","itemFeaturedNotice":"","itemAuthor":"","itemFontResizer":"","itemPrintButton":"","itemEmailButton":"","itemSocialButton":"","itemVideoAnchor":"","itemImageGalleryAnchor":"","itemCommentsAnchor":"","itemRating":"","itemImage":"","itemImgSize":"","itemImageMainCaption":"","itemImageMainCredits":"","itemIntroText":"","itemFullText":"","itemExtraFields":"","itemDateModified":"","itemHits":"","itemCategory":"","itemTags":"","itemAttachments":"","itemAttachmentsCounter":"","itemVideo":"","itemVideoWidth":"","itemVideoHeight":"","itemAudioWidth":"","itemAudioHeight":"","itemVideoAutoPlay":"","itemVideoCaption":"","itemVideoCredits":"","itemImageGallery":"","itemImageGalleryWidth":"","itemImageGalleryHeight":"","itemNavigation":"","itemComments":"","itemTwitterButton":"","itemFacebookButton":"","itemGooglePlusOneButton":"","itemAuthorBlock":"","itemAuthorImage":"","itemAuthorDescription":"","itemAuthorURL":"","itemAuthorEmail":"","itemAuthorLatest":"","itemAuthorLatestLimit":"","itemRelated":"","itemRelatedLimit":"","itemRelatedTitle":"","itemRelatedCategory":"","itemRelatedImageSize":"","itemRelatedIntrotext":"","itemRelatedFulltext":"","itemRelatedAuthor":"","itemRelatedMedia":"","itemRelatedImageGallery":"","itemK2Plugins":""}', '', 'robots=\nauthor=', '', '', 'en-GB'),
(105, 'Qualitative characteristics', 'qualitative-characteristics-en', 29, 1, '<p>The special composition of the Natural Mineral Water “ZAGORI” is characterized by low sodium content, which renders it suitable for a low sodium diet.</p>\r\n<p>The characterization of the water as “low content in salt” is owed to the fact that the product meets the corresponding criterion of the Presidential Decree 433/83 and the Directive 2009/54/ΕΚ, where the content of minerals calculated as fixed residue should be 180 mg/lt. It is about a quantity, which does not approach even half of the upper estimated limit, which corresponds to 500 mg/lt.</p>\r\n<p>At the same time, the water content in Sodium (Na+) is less than the corresponding Legislative limit of 20 mg/lt, and in particular it rises to 2 mg/lt.</p>\r\n<p>Its calcium content (62,4 mg/l Ca++) contributes to the maintenance of the good health of bones, teeth as well as the proper functioning of the muscular and nervous system.</p>\r\n<p>The values of the above, as well as the values of all the parameters, indicate that it is about digestible water, the daily use of which does not place excessive quantities from an element to the human organism.</p>\r\n<p> </p>', '', NULL, NULL, '[]', '', '2016-11-25 15:51:31', 191, '', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2016-11-25 15:53:52', 191, '2016-11-17 14:35:30', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1, 2, 0, 0, '', '', '', '', 2, '{"catItemTitle":"","catItemTitleLinked":"","catItemFeaturedNotice":"","catItemAuthor":"","catItemDateCreated":"","catItemRating":"","catItemImage":"","catItemIntroText":"","catItemExtraFields":"","catItemHits":"","catItemCategory":"","catItemTags":"","catItemAttachments":"","catItemAttachmentsCounter":"","catItemVideo":"","catItemVideoWidth":"","catItemVideoHeight":"","catItemAudioWidth":"","catItemAudioHeight":"","catItemVideoAutoPlay":"","catItemImageGallery":"","catItemImageGalleryWidth":"","catItemImageGalleryHeight":"","catItemDateModified":"","catItemReadMore":"","catItemCommentsAnchor":"","catItemK2Plugins":"","itemDateCreated":"","itemTitle":"","itemFeaturedNotice":"","itemAuthor":"","itemFontResizer":"","itemPrintButton":"","itemEmailButton":"","itemSocialButton":"","itemVideoAnchor":"","itemImageGalleryAnchor":"","itemCommentsAnchor":"","itemRating":"","itemImage":"","itemImgSize":"","itemImageMainCaption":"","itemImageMainCredits":"","itemIntroText":"","itemFullText":"","itemExtraFields":"","itemDateModified":"","itemHits":"","itemCategory":"","itemTags":"","itemAttachments":"","itemAttachmentsCounter":"","itemVideo":"","itemVideoWidth":"","itemVideoHeight":"","itemAudioWidth":"","itemAudioHeight":"","itemVideoAutoPlay":"","itemVideoCaption":"","itemVideoCredits":"","itemImageGallery":"","itemImageGalleryWidth":"","itemImageGalleryHeight":"","itemNavigation":"","itemComments":"","itemTwitterButton":"","itemFacebookButton":"","itemGooglePlusOneButton":"","itemAuthorBlock":"","itemAuthorImage":"","itemAuthorDescription":"","itemAuthorURL":"","itemAuthorEmail":"","itemAuthorLatest":"","itemAuthorLatestLimit":"","itemRelated":"","itemRelatedLimit":"","itemRelatedTitle":"","itemRelatedCategory":"","itemRelatedImageSize":"","itemRelatedIntrotext":"","itemRelatedFulltext":"","itemRelatedAuthor":"","itemRelatedMedia":"","itemRelatedImageGallery":"","itemK2Plugins":""}', '', 'robots=\nauthor=', '', '', 'en-GB'),
(106, 'Certifications - Quality', 'certifications-quality', 29, 1, '<p>The Quality Policy of primary importance, for which has been committed the Management of the Company in order to keep as a priority towards every consumer, sets the standards of the quality to the highest rank. This constitutes also the guarantee that the production processes do not influence to a minimum any property and condition that has the water inside the underground aquafer until the sealing of each bottle that will contain it.</p>\r\n<p>Based on this Policy, the Company cooperates continuously and is available to all the state control bodies, as imposed by the national and the European legislation.</p>\r\n<p>Within this framework, CHITOS S.A. has constant cooperations with the CHEMICAL SERVICES OF IOANNINA (GENERAL CHEMICAL STATE LABORATORY), with the LABORATORY OF HYGIENE OF THE MEDICAL SCHOOL AT THE UNIVERSITY OF IOANNINA, as well as the accredited laboratories of analyses abroad, of international range which certifies the quality of its product and guarantees the safety of the consumers.</p>\r\n<p>In addition, the well staffed departments of Quality Assurance and Quality Control supervise, control and monitor continuously all the procedures from the spring until the final product, as well as the quality of the packaging materials in suitably equipped Laboratories of the Company, in order to meet the high specifications and the standards set by CHITOS S.A. which have made the company first to the choice of the consumers.</p>\r\n<p>At the same time, along with its guaranteed quality, due to the exceptional geological conditions of Epirus, “ZAGORI” water is constantly subjected to strict controls, according always with the requirements of the standards EN ISO 9001:2008 and EN ISO 22000:2005, as well as the EBWA Code of Hygiene Practice. The proper application of the above standards was certified by the accredited certification bodies TUV HELLAS - TUV NORD and NSF INTERNATIONAL, which concern the management of hygiene, safety and quality of foods.</p>', '', NULL, NULL, '[]', '', '2016-11-25 15:51:31', 191, '', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2016-11-25 15:55:34', 191, '2016-11-17 14:38:22', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1, 3, 0, 0, '', '', '', '', 0, '{"catItemTitle":"","catItemTitleLinked":"","catItemFeaturedNotice":"","catItemAuthor":"","catItemDateCreated":"","catItemRating":"","catItemImage":"","catItemIntroText":"","catItemExtraFields":"","catItemHits":"","catItemCategory":"","catItemTags":"","catItemAttachments":"","catItemAttachmentsCounter":"","catItemVideo":"","catItemVideoWidth":"","catItemVideoHeight":"","catItemAudioWidth":"","catItemAudioHeight":"","catItemVideoAutoPlay":"","catItemImageGallery":"","catItemImageGalleryWidth":"","catItemImageGalleryHeight":"","catItemDateModified":"","catItemReadMore":"","catItemCommentsAnchor":"","catItemK2Plugins":"","itemDateCreated":"","itemTitle":"","itemFeaturedNotice":"","itemAuthor":"","itemFontResizer":"","itemPrintButton":"","itemEmailButton":"","itemSocialButton":"","itemVideoAnchor":"","itemImageGalleryAnchor":"","itemCommentsAnchor":"","itemRating":"","itemImage":"","itemImgSize":"","itemImageMainCaption":"","itemImageMainCredits":"","itemIntroText":"","itemFullText":"","itemExtraFields":"","itemDateModified":"","itemHits":"","itemCategory":"","itemTags":"","itemAttachments":"","itemAttachmentsCounter":"","itemVideo":"","itemVideoWidth":"","itemVideoHeight":"","itemAudioWidth":"","itemAudioHeight":"","itemVideoAutoPlay":"","itemVideoCaption":"","itemVideoCredits":"","itemImageGallery":"","itemImageGalleryWidth":"","itemImageGalleryHeight":"","itemNavigation":"","itemComments":"","itemTwitterButton":"","itemFacebookButton":"","itemGooglePlusOneButton":"","itemAuthorBlock":"","itemAuthorImage":"","itemAuthorDescription":"","itemAuthorURL":"","itemAuthorEmail":"","itemAuthorLatest":"","itemAuthorLatestLimit":"","itemRelated":"","itemRelatedLimit":"","itemRelatedTitle":"","itemRelatedCategory":"","itemRelatedImageSize":"","itemRelatedIntrotext":"","itemRelatedFulltext":"","itemRelatedAuthor":"","itemRelatedMedia":"","itemRelatedImageGallery":"","itemK2Plugins":""}', '', 'robots=\nauthor=', '', '', 'en-GB'),
(107, 'The plant', 'plant-en', 29, 1, '<p>The bottling plant is situated at an altitude of 485 m to the feet of the mountain Mitsikeli in absolute harmony with the environment.</p>\r\n<p>All the procedures – bottling, labeling, arrangement, quality control – are made with a modern equipment of cutting edge technology.</p>\r\n<p>Through vertical integration and supporting of the operation of both fillers CHITOS S.A. has also a third industrial plant to the Industrial Zone (VI.PΕ.) of Ioannina, which has automated manufacture of plastic packaging materials pet – preforms and caps. The manufacture of packaging materials is made by selecting the raw materials of optimum quality with an installed system of continuous controls of final products, which are intended to protect and keep unchanged the character of water inside the bottle.</p>', '', NULL, NULL, '[]', '', '2016-11-25 15:51:31', 191, '', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2016-11-25 15:56:29', 191, '2016-11-17 14:41:07', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1, 4, 0, 0, '', '', '', '', 3, '{"catItemTitle":"","catItemTitleLinked":"","catItemFeaturedNotice":"","catItemAuthor":"","catItemDateCreated":"","catItemRating":"","catItemImage":"","catItemIntroText":"","catItemExtraFields":"","catItemHits":"","catItemCategory":"","catItemTags":"","catItemAttachments":"","catItemAttachmentsCounter":"","catItemVideo":"","catItemVideoWidth":"","catItemVideoHeight":"","catItemAudioWidth":"","catItemAudioHeight":"","catItemVideoAutoPlay":"","catItemImageGallery":"","catItemImageGalleryWidth":"","catItemImageGalleryHeight":"","catItemDateModified":"","catItemReadMore":"","catItemCommentsAnchor":"","catItemK2Plugins":"","itemDateCreated":"","itemTitle":"","itemFeaturedNotice":"","itemAuthor":"","itemFontResizer":"","itemPrintButton":"","itemEmailButton":"","itemSocialButton":"","itemVideoAnchor":"","itemImageGalleryAnchor":"","itemCommentsAnchor":"","itemRating":"","itemImage":"","itemImgSize":"","itemImageMainCaption":"","itemImageMainCredits":"","itemIntroText":"","itemFullText":"","itemExtraFields":"","itemDateModified":"","itemHits":"","itemCategory":"","itemTags":"","itemAttachments":"","itemAttachmentsCounter":"","itemVideo":"","itemVideoWidth":"","itemVideoHeight":"","itemAudioWidth":"","itemAudioHeight":"","itemVideoAutoPlay":"","itemVideoCaption":"","itemVideoCredits":"","itemImageGallery":"","itemImageGalleryWidth":"","itemImageGalleryHeight":"","itemNavigation":"","itemComments":"","itemTwitterButton":"","itemFacebookButton":"","itemGooglePlusOneButton":"","itemAuthorBlock":"","itemAuthorImage":"","itemAuthorDescription":"","itemAuthorURL":"","itemAuthorEmail":"","itemAuthorLatest":"","itemAuthorLatestLimit":"","itemRelated":"","itemRelatedLimit":"","itemRelatedTitle":"","itemRelatedCategory":"","itemRelatedImageSize":"","itemRelatedIntrotext":"","itemRelatedFulltext":"","itemRelatedAuthor":"","itemRelatedMedia":"","itemRelatedImageGallery":"","itemK2Plugins":""}', '', 'robots=\nauthor=', '', '', 'en-GB'),
(108, 'The bottling', 'bottling-en', 29, 1, '<p>The bottling of  “ZAGORI” water is made with high tech machines, where it takes place an on site configuration of bottle and simultaneous bottling and capping, in an environment completely closed, without mediating the human factor at any stage. Each bottle is manufactured 3 seconds before the water that comes directly from the underground aquifer, enters to the interior, fills it up and is sealed directly by the cap.</p>', '', NULL, NULL, '[]', '', '2016-11-25 15:51:31', 191, '', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2016-11-25 15:57:16', 191, '2016-11-17 14:46:18', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1, 5, 0, 0, '', '', '', '', 1, '{"catItemTitle":"","catItemTitleLinked":"","catItemFeaturedNotice":"","catItemAuthor":"","catItemDateCreated":"","catItemRating":"","catItemImage":"","catItemIntroText":"","catItemExtraFields":"","catItemHits":"","catItemCategory":"","catItemTags":"","catItemAttachments":"","catItemAttachmentsCounter":"","catItemVideo":"","catItemVideoWidth":"","catItemVideoHeight":"","catItemAudioWidth":"","catItemAudioHeight":"","catItemVideoAutoPlay":"","catItemImageGallery":"","catItemImageGalleryWidth":"","catItemImageGalleryHeight":"","catItemDateModified":"","catItemReadMore":"","catItemCommentsAnchor":"","catItemK2Plugins":"","itemDateCreated":"","itemTitle":"","itemFeaturedNotice":"","itemAuthor":"","itemFontResizer":"","itemPrintButton":"","itemEmailButton":"","itemSocialButton":"","itemVideoAnchor":"","itemImageGalleryAnchor":"","itemCommentsAnchor":"","itemRating":"","itemImage":"","itemImgSize":"","itemImageMainCaption":"","itemImageMainCredits":"","itemIntroText":"","itemFullText":"","itemExtraFields":"","itemDateModified":"","itemHits":"","itemCategory":"","itemTags":"","itemAttachments":"","itemAttachmentsCounter":"","itemVideo":"","itemVideoWidth":"","itemVideoHeight":"","itemAudioWidth":"","itemAudioHeight":"","itemVideoAutoPlay":"","itemVideoCaption":"","itemVideoCredits":"","itemImageGallery":"","itemImageGalleryWidth":"","itemImageGalleryHeight":"","itemNavigation":"","itemComments":"","itemTwitterButton":"","itemFacebookButton":"","itemGooglePlusOneButton":"","itemAuthorBlock":"","itemAuthorImage":"","itemAuthorDescription":"","itemAuthorURL":"","itemAuthorEmail":"","itemAuthorLatest":"","itemAuthorLatestLimit":"","itemRelated":"","itemRelatedLimit":"","itemRelatedTitle":"","itemRelatedCategory":"","itemRelatedImageSize":"","itemRelatedIntrotext":"","itemRelatedFulltext":"","itemRelatedAuthor":"","itemRelatedMedia":"","itemRelatedImageGallery":"","itemK2Plugins":""}', '', 'robots=\nauthor=', '', '', 'en-GB'),
(109, 'Les sources', 'springs-fr', 35, 1, '<p>La Société Anonyme CHITOS possède à sa disposition deux sources reconnues d’eau naturelle et minérale qui se trouvent aux pieds du mont Mitsikeli à Zagorochoria.</p>\r\n<p>La couche aquifère d’où on puise l’Eau ZAGORI -selon des études hydrogéologiques et des analyses spéciales- est protégée de tout impact extérieur et contre la pollution de l’environnement tandis que sa construction naturelle garantit une qualité invariable. Les formations géologiques de la région offrent un contenu spécifique de l’eau riche en éléments métaux et non métaux en créant son goût équilibré alors qu’elles fonctionnent comme des filtres naturels lors de son parcours vers la bassine aquifère souterraine  où elle est retenue pendant toute l’année. De cette façon elle est débarrassée de l’existence des microorganismes pathogènes.    </p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p><img title="Η διαδρομή του νερού" src="images/diagramma.jpg" alt="Η διαδρομή του νερού" width="600" height="374" /></p>', '', NULL, NULL, '[]', '', '2016-11-25 15:59:40', 191, '', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2016-11-25 16:07:23', 191, '2016-11-17 14:29:10', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1, 1, 0, 0, '', '', '', '', 1, '{"catItemTitle":"","catItemTitleLinked":"","catItemFeaturedNotice":"","catItemAuthor":"","catItemDateCreated":"","catItemRating":"","catItemImage":"","catItemIntroText":"","catItemExtraFields":"","catItemHits":"","catItemCategory":"","catItemTags":"","catItemAttachments":"","catItemAttachmentsCounter":"","catItemVideo":"","catItemVideoWidth":"","catItemVideoHeight":"","catItemAudioWidth":"","catItemAudioHeight":"","catItemVideoAutoPlay":"","catItemImageGallery":"","catItemImageGalleryWidth":"","catItemImageGalleryHeight":"","catItemDateModified":"","catItemReadMore":"","catItemCommentsAnchor":"","catItemK2Plugins":"","itemDateCreated":"","itemTitle":"","itemFeaturedNotice":"","itemAuthor":"","itemFontResizer":"","itemPrintButton":"","itemEmailButton":"","itemSocialButton":"","itemVideoAnchor":"","itemImageGalleryAnchor":"","itemCommentsAnchor":"","itemRating":"","itemImage":"","itemImgSize":"","itemImageMainCaption":"","itemImageMainCredits":"","itemIntroText":"","itemFullText":"","itemExtraFields":"","itemDateModified":"","itemHits":"","itemCategory":"","itemTags":"","itemAttachments":"","itemAttachmentsCounter":"","itemVideo":"","itemVideoWidth":"","itemVideoHeight":"","itemAudioWidth":"","itemAudioHeight":"","itemVideoAutoPlay":"","itemVideoCaption":"","itemVideoCredits":"","itemImageGallery":"","itemImageGalleryWidth":"","itemImageGalleryHeight":"","itemNavigation":"","itemComments":"","itemTwitterButton":"","itemFacebookButton":"","itemGooglePlusOneButton":"","itemAuthorBlock":"","itemAuthorImage":"","itemAuthorDescription":"","itemAuthorURL":"","itemAuthorEmail":"","itemAuthorLatest":"","itemAuthorLatestLimit":"","itemRelated":"","itemRelatedLimit":"","itemRelatedTitle":"","itemRelatedCategory":"","itemRelatedImageSize":"","itemRelatedIntrotext":"","itemRelatedFulltext":"","itemRelatedAuthor":"","itemRelatedMedia":"","itemRelatedImageGallery":"","itemK2Plugins":""}', '', 'robots=\nauthor=', '', '', 'fr-FR'),
(110, 'Traits de qualité', 'qualitative-characteristics-fr', 35, 1, '<p>La texture spéciale de l’Eau Naturelle et Minérale « ZAGORI » est qualifiée d’une basse contenance en sels en la rendant convenable pour un régime pauvre en sodium (Na).</p>\r\n<p>La caractérisation de l’eau comme une « eau de basse contenance en sels » est due au fait que le produit correspond à des critères du Décret de la République 433/83 et de la directive 2009/54/UE où la contenance en matières minérales bien mesurée devrait présenter un résidu stable au niveau de 180 mg/It. En particulier, il s’agit d’une quantité qui ne touche ni à la moitié le niveau maximum prévu qui s’avère à 500mg/It.</p>\r\n<p>Parallèlement, la contenance de l’eau en sodium (Na) est plus basse que la limite légale de 20mg/It et elle s’avère surtout à 2 mg/It.</p>\r\n<p>Sa contenance en calcium (62,4 mg/I Ca++) contribue au maintient de la bonne santé des os, des dents mais aussi au bon fonctionnement du système musculaire et nerveux.</p>\r\n<p>Les prix des données plus haut et de l’ensemble des paramètres démontrent que l’eau Zagori est propre pour la digestion stomacale et sa consommation quotidienne ne fournit pas à l’organisme humain de grandes quantités de certains éléments.</p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p> </p>', '', NULL, NULL, '[]', '', '2016-11-25 15:59:40', 191, '', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2016-11-25 16:08:18', 191, '2016-11-17 14:35:30', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1, 2, 0, 0, '', '', '', '', 2, '{"catItemTitle":"","catItemTitleLinked":"","catItemFeaturedNotice":"","catItemAuthor":"","catItemDateCreated":"","catItemRating":"","catItemImage":"","catItemIntroText":"","catItemExtraFields":"","catItemHits":"","catItemCategory":"","catItemTags":"","catItemAttachments":"","catItemAttachmentsCounter":"","catItemVideo":"","catItemVideoWidth":"","catItemVideoHeight":"","catItemAudioWidth":"","catItemAudioHeight":"","catItemVideoAutoPlay":"","catItemImageGallery":"","catItemImageGalleryWidth":"","catItemImageGalleryHeight":"