(121, 'CHITOS S.A., one of the Diamonds of the Greek Business', 'the-most-admired-enterprises-2013-en', 48, 1, '<p>Awarding of the prize “Diamonds - The Most Admired Enterprises 2013”</p>\r\n', '\r\n<p>For another year CHITOS S.A. and ZAGORI Natural Mineral Water, was awarded as one of the healthiest growing businesses of the country during the event of SΤΑΤ ΒΑΝΚ with subject, the Diamonds of the Greek Economy for 2013. The selection of CHITOS S.A. was made among the largest businesses of the country, based on ten strict economic criteria which confirm the reliability and their healthy course.</p>\r\n<p>CHITOS S.A strengthens its leading position in the Greek market, by investing in new building facilities in Greece, by creating new job positions, while at the same time it kept intact the rate of wages of its employees for 2013, by absorbing entirely the reductions of the last memorandum. Simultaneously, it has more extroversion that distinguishes it during the last two years by exporting its product to more than 18 countries while are expected to open up and other markets until the end of the year.</p>\r\n<p>The award for CHITOS S.A. was taken by the Sales Manager of the company Mr Tryfonas Tzelis, who among others stated: “In a period where the country experiences an unprecedented recession, companies such as CHITOS S.A. seem to constitute the guide for the exit from the crisis and keep alive the hope that Greece will return to growth rates and welfare. It is our great honour to constitute one of the diamonds of the necklace that the Greek economy should wear in order to shine again”.</p>', NULL, NULL, '[]', '', '2016-11-28 13:23:04', 191, '', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2016-11-28 13:27:40', 191, '2016-11-21 16:45:35', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1, 3, 0, 0, '', '', '', '', 0, '{"catItemTitle":"","catItemTitleLinked":"","catItemFeaturedNotice":"","catItemAuthor":"","catItemDateCreated":"","catItemRating":"","catItemImage":"","catItemIntroText":"","catItemExtraFields":"","catItemHits":"","catItemCategory":"","catItemTags":"","catItemAttachments":"","catItemAttachmentsCounter":"","catItemVideo":"","catItemVideoWidth":"","catItemVideoHeight":"","catItemAudioWidth":"","catItemAudioHeight":"","catItemVideoAutoPlay":"","catItemImageGallery":"","catItemImageGalleryWidth":"","catItemImageGalleryHeight":"","catItemDateModified":"","catItemReadMore":"","catItemCommentsAnchor":"","catItemK2Plugins":"","itemDateCreated":"","itemTitle":"","itemFeaturedNotice":"","itemAuthor":"","itemFontResizer":"","itemPrintButton":"","itemEmailButton":"","itemSocialButton":"","itemVideoAnchor":"","itemImageGalleryAnchor":"","itemCommentsAnchor":"","itemRating":"","itemImage":"","itemImgSize":"","itemImageMainCaption":"","itemImageMainCredits":"","itemIntroText":"","itemFullText":"","itemExtraFields":"","itemDateModified":"","itemHits":"","itemCategory":"","itemTags":"","itemAttachments":"","itemAttachmentsCounter":"","itemVideo":"","itemVideoWidth":"","itemVideoHeight":"","itemAudioWidth":"","itemAudioHeight":"","itemVideoAutoPlay":"","itemVideoCaption":"","itemVideoCredits":"","itemImageGallery":"","itemImageGalleryWidth":"","itemImageGalleryHeight":"","itemNavigation":"","itemComments":"","itemTwitterButton":"","itemFacebookButton":"","itemGooglePlusOneButton":"","itemAuthorBlock":"","itemAuthorImage":"","itemAuthorDescription":"","itemAuthorURL":"","itemAuthorEmail":"","itemAuthorLatest":"","itemAuthorLatestLimit":"","itemRelated":"","itemRelatedLimit":"","itemRelatedTitle":"","itemRelatedCategory":"","itemRelatedImageSize":"","itemRelatedIntrotext":"","itemRelatedFulltext":"","itemRelatedAuthor":"","itemRelatedMedia":"","itemRelatedImageGallery":"","itemK2Plugins":""}', '', 'robots=\nauthor=', '', '', 'en-GB'),
(122, 'CHITOS S.A. / ZAGORI Natural Mineral Water absorbs the new reduction of wages by investing, in practice, in human resources', 'i-xitos-a-v-e-e-kai-to-fysiko-metalliko-nero-zagori-en', 48, 1, '<p>CHITOS S.A. and the natural mineral water ZAGORI, on the occasion of the annual corporate event which was made for the cutting of the New Year’s pie, were analyzed the targets and the perspectives for the New Year.</p>\r\n', '\r\n<p> In the framework of which Mr Nikolaos Chitos has announced the following : “The company will absorb entirely the new reductions of wages resulting from the implementation of the memorandum (at 01/01/2013) and concern not only the increase of income tax as well as the social security contributions. We hope as a company to continue constituting a lighthouse of hope and optimism for a better tomorrow″.</p>\r\n<p>At a time where the adverse economic climate has as a result to close down many businesses, the exodus of multinational groups from the country, the decline in employment and the increase in unemployment, there are Greek companies which continue to invest and to grow maintaining at the same time all the principles of the healthy entrepreneurship.</p>\r\n<p>A real proof constitutes the fact, that throughout this period that the low wage cost is considered by many businesses as an effective measure for their sustainability, CHITOS S.A. proceeds to recruitments while it has not proceed to any reduction, not only to the salaries but also to the number of its employees.</p>\r\n<p>In this way, CHITOS S.A. proves in practice that its most important capital is human resources, while the preservation of the employment, the welfare and the quality of life in Greece, in total, constitutes for the company a prerequisite for the encouragement of the consumption, the sustainable development and the progress.</p>', NULL, NULL, '[]', '', '2016-11-28 13:23:04', 191, '', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2016-11-28 13:29:25', 191, '2016-11-21 15:53:21', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1, 4, 0, 0, '', '', '', '', 0, '{"catItemTitle":"","catItemTitleLinked":"","catItemFeaturedNotice":"","catItemAuthor":"","catItemDateCreated":"","catItemRating":"","catItemImage":"","catItemIntroText":"","catItemExtraFields":"","catItemHits":"","catItemCategory":"","catItemTags":"","catItemAttachments":"","catItemAttachmentsCounter":"","catItemVideo":"","catItemVideoWidth":"","catItemVideoHeight":"","catItemAudioWidth":"","catItemAudioHeight":"","catItemVideoAutoPlay":"","catItemImageGallery":"","catItemImageGalleryWidth":"","catItemImageGalleryHeight":"","catItemDateModified":"","catItemReadMore":"","catItemCommentsAnchor":"","catItemK2Plugins":"","itemDateCreated":"","itemTitle":"","itemFeaturedNotice":"","itemAuthor":"","itemFontResizer":"","itemPrintButton":"","itemEmailButton":"","itemSocialButton":"","itemVideoAnchor":"","itemImageGalleryAnchor":"","itemCommentsAnchor":"","itemRating":"","itemImage":"","itemImgSize":"","itemImageMainCaption":"","itemImageMainCredits":"","itemIntroText":"","itemFullText":"","itemExtraFields":"","itemDateModified":"","itemHits":"","itemCategory":"","itemTags":"","itemAttachments":"","itemAttachmentsCounter":"","itemVideo":"","itemVideoWidth":"","itemVideoHeight":"","itemAudioWidth":"","itemAudioHeight":"","itemVideoAutoPlay":"","itemVideoCaption":"","itemVideoCredits":"","itemImageGallery":"","itemImageGalleryWidth":"","itemImageGalleryHeight":"","itemNavigation":"","itemComments":"","itemTwitterButton":"","itemFacebookButton":"","itemGooglePlusOneButton":"","itemAuthorBlock":"","itemAuthorImage":"","itemAuthorDescription":"","itemAuthorURL":"","itemAuthorEmail":"","itemAuthorLatest":"","itemAuthorLatestLimit":"","itemRelated":"","itemRelatedLimit":"","itemRelatedTitle":"","itemRelatedCategory":"","itemRelatedImageSize":"","itemRelatedIntrotext":"","itemRelatedFulltext":"","itemRelatedAuthor":"","itemRelatedMedia":"","itemRelatedImageGallery":"","itemK2Plugins":""}', '', 'robots=\nauthor=', '', '', 'en-GB')