(125, 'CHITOS SA distinguished as "Diamond Greek Economy" for 4th time', 'the-most-admired-enterprises-2014-fr', 51, 1, '<p>Awarding of the prize “Diamonds - The Most Admired Enterprises 2014”</p>\r\n', '\r\n<p>For the fourth consecutive year CHITOS SA with natural mineral water ZAGORI, awarded as one of the healthiest growing enterprises in Greece within the institution "Diamonds of Greek Companies" for 2014.</p>\r\n<p>The CHITOS SA continues to strengthen its leading position in the Greek market, investing in growth, innovation and technology, launching new products, creating new jobs and keeping intact the payroll of their employees. The company is continuing to focus on expanding exports with its products today, in 20 countries worldwide.</p>\r\n<p>The award for the CHITOS SA received by Mr. Nikos Chitos, vice president of the company, which, inter alia, he stated: "The current distinction which is obtained for the fourth consecutive year is an honor for our company and has significant value as encompassing all those values that dictate that we continue development initiative by investing in extraversion and innovation”.</p>', NULL, NULL, '[]', '', '2016-11-28 13:31:04', 191, '', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2016-11-28 13:32:15', 191, '2016-11-21 16:49:51', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1, 3, 0, 0, '', '', '', '', 0, '{"catItemTitle":"","catItemTitleLinked":"","catItemFeaturedNotice":"","catItemAuthor":"","catItemDateCreated":"","catItemRating":"","catItemImage":"","catItemIntroText":"","catItemExtraFields":"","catItemHits":"","catItemCategory":"","catItemTags":"","catItemAttachments":"","catItemAttachmentsCounter":"","catItemVideo":"","catItemVideoWidth":"","catItemVideoHeight":"","catItemAudioWidth":"","catItemAudioHeight":"","catItemVideoAutoPlay":"","catItemImageGallery":"","catItemImageGalleryWidth":"","catItemImageGalleryHeight":"","catItemDateModified":"","catItemReadMore":"","catItemCommentsAnchor":"","catItemK2Plugins":"","itemDateCreated":"","itemTitle":"","