(168, 'ANNONCE', 'anakoinwsh-fr', 52, 1, '<p style="text-align: justify;">La Société Anonyme CHITOS informe ses consommateurs sur :</p>\r\n', '\r\n<p>• La fin de sa collaboration avec l’entreprise Rainbow Group – Rainbow Waters qui était chargée de la délivrance exclusive de l’emballage «ZAGORI 18,9 lt – produit destiné à des fontaines d’eau réfrigérée» dans la région d’Attique.<br /> • Le transfert de capitaux proportionnés à la Société Anonyme CHITOS au nom du capital de l’entreprise « ZAGORI – RAINBOW GROUP » vers l’entreprise « RAINBOW WATERS ».</p>\r\n<p>Par conséquent, la Société Anonyme CHITOS arrête la production et la mise en vente de l’Eau Naturelle et Minérale « ZAGORI » en bouteilles retournables en plastique destinées à des fontaines d’eau réfrigérée (watercoolers).</p>\r\n<p>La suppression de cette collaboration concerne les différentes priorités stratégiques de deux entreprises. La Société Anonyme CHITOS continue à investir à des solutions novatrices et à des emballages en penchant son intérêt à de nouveaux emballages respectueux vers l’environnement contenant l’EAU NATURELLE ET MINERALE « ZAGORI » en respectant toujours le consommateur.</p>\r\n<p>On voudrait remercier tous les consommateurs pour leur confiance et leur préférence pour cet emballage au cours de ces dernières 12 années de son cycle de vie. Toute la variété disponible en emballage « Zagori » vous pouvez la trouver dans tous les points de vente en Grèce. La valeur et la qualité de l’Eau Naturelle et Minérale ZAGORI sont révélées grâce à la diversité de ses 11 emballages qui correspondent à chaque cas de consommation à n’importe quel moment de la journée.</p>', NULL, NULL, '[]', '', '2015-03-11 15:41:24', 191, '', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2016-11-28 15:47:29', 191, '2016-11-22 11:39:11', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1, 1, 0, 0, '', '', '', '', 0, '{"catItemTitle":"","catItemTitleLinked":"","catItemFeaturedNotice":"","catItemAuthor":"","catItemDateCreated":"","catItemRating":"","catItemImage":"","catItemIntroText":"","catItemExtraFields":"","catItemHits":"","catItemCategory":"","catItemTags":"","catItemAttachments":"","catItemAttachmentsCounter":"","catItemVideo":"","catItemVideoWidth":"","catItemVideoHeight":"","catItemAudioWidth":"","catItemAudioHeight":"","catItemVideoAutoPlay":"","catItemImageGallery":"","catItemImageGalleryWidth":"","catItemImageGalleryHeight":"","catItemDateModified":"","catItemReadMore":"","catItemCommentsAnchor":"","catItemK2Plugins":"","itemDateCreated":"","itemTitle":"","itemFeaturedNotice":"","itemAuthor":"","itemFontResizer":"","itemPrintButton":"","itemEmailButton":"","itemSocialButton":"","itemVideoAnchor":"","itemImageGalleryAnchor":"","itemCommentsAnchor":"","itemRating":"","itemImage":"","itemImgSize":"","itemImageMainCaption":"","itemImageMainCredits":"","itemIntroText":"","itemFullText":"","itemExtraFields":"","itemDateModified":"","itemHits":"","itemCategory":"","itemTags":"","itemAttachments":"","itemAttachmentsCounter":"","itemVideo":"","itemVideoWidth":"","itemVideoHeight":"","itemAudioWidth":"","itemAudioHeight":"","itemVideoAutoPlay":"","itemVideoCaption":"","itemVideoCredits":"","itemImageGallery":"","itemImageGalleryWidth":"","itemImageGalleryHeight":"","itemNavigation":"","itemComments":"","itemTwitterButton":"","itemFacebookButton":"","itemGooglePlusOneButton":"","itemAuthorBlock":"","itemAuthorImage":"","itemAuthorDescription":"","itemAuthorURL":"","itemAuthorEmail":"","itemAuthorLatest":"","itemAuthorLatestLimit":"","itemRelated":"","itemRelatedLimit":"","itemRelatedTitle":"","itemRelatedCategory":"","itemRelatedImageSize":"","itemRelatedIntrotext":"","itemRelatedFulltext":"","itemRelatedAuthor":"","itemRelatedMedia":"","itemRelatedImageGallery":"","itemK2Plugins":""}', '', 'robots=\nauthor=', '', '', 'fr-FR'),
(169, 'BEKANNTGABE', 'anakoinwsh', 55, 1, '<p style="text-align: justify;">CHITOS AG informiert ihre Verbraucher über:</p>\r\n', '\r\n<p>• das Ende der Zusammenarbeit mit der Firma Rainbow Group - Rainbow Waters, die für den exklusiven Vertrieb der Verpackung der „18,9 lt ZAGORI – Produkt für Wasserspender“ in der Region von Attika galt<br /> • die Übertragung der Aktienanteils der CHITOS AG am Aktienkapital der Gesellschaft „ZAGORI-RAINBOW-GROUP“ an die RAINBOW WATERS.</p>\r\n<p>Somit stoppt CHITOS AG die Produktion und den Vertrieb des natürlichen Mineralwasser „ZAGORI“ in Mehrwegplastikflaschen von 18,9 Litern für Wasserkühler.</p>\r\n<p>Die Unterbrechung der Zusammenarbeit ist mit den unterschiedlichen strategischen Prioritäten der beiden Unternehmen verbunden.</p>\r\n<p>CHITOS AG investiert weiterhin in innovativen Lösungen und Verpackung, indem es sich auf neue, umweltfreundliche Verpackungen für das natürliche Mineralwasser „ZAGORI“, immer mit Respekt für die Verbraucher, konzentriert.</p>\r\n<p>Wir danken den Verbrauchern für ihr Vertrauen und Vorzug, den sie dieser Verpackung den vergangenen 12 Jahren gezeigt haben. Die verschiedenen Verpackungen des Wassers ZAGORI werden sie an allen Verkaufsstellen finden. Der Wert und die Qualität des natürlichen Mineralwassers ZAGORI, wird durch die verschiedene 11 Verpackungen gedeckt, die jedes Bedürfnis zu jeder Zeit des Tages deckt.</p>', NULL, NULL, '[]', '', '2015-03-11 15:41:43', 191, '', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2016-11-28 15:47:05', 191, '2016-11-22 11:39:11', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1, 1, 0, 0, '', '', '', '', 0, '{"catItemTitle":"","catItemTitleLinked":"","catItemFeaturedNotice":"","catItemAuthor":"","catItemDateCreated":"","catItemRating":"","catItemImage":"","catItemIntroText":"","catItemExtraFields":"","catItemHits":"","catItemCategory":"","catItemTags":"","catItemAttachments":"","catItemAttachmentsCounter":"","catItemVideo":"","catItemVideoWidth":"","catItemVideoHeight":"","catItemAudioWidth":"","catItemAudioHeight":"","catItemVideoAutoPlay":"","catItemImageGallery":"","catItemImageGalleryWidth":"","catItemImageGalleryHeight":"","catItemDateModified":"","catItemReadMore":"","catItemCommentsAnchor":"","catItemK2Plugins":"","itemDateCreated":"","itemTitle":"","itemFeaturedNotice":"","itemAuthor":"","itemFontResizer":"","itemPrintButton":"","itemEmailButton":"","itemSocialButton":"","itemVideoAnchor":"","itemImageGalleryAnchor":"","itemCommentsAnchor":"","itemRating":"","itemImage":"","itemImgSize":"","itemImageMainCaption":"","itemImageMainCredits":"","itemIntroText":"","itemFullText":"","itemExtraFields":"","itemDateModified":"","itemHits":"","itemCategory":"","itemTags":"","itemAttachments":"","itemAttachmentsCounter":"","itemVideo":"","itemVideoWidth":"","itemVideoHeight":"","itemAudioWidth":"","itemAudioHeight":"","itemVideoAutoPlay":"","itemVideoCaption":"","itemVideoCredits":"","itemImageGallery":"","itemImageGalleryWidth":"","itemImageGalleryHeight":"","itemNavigation":"","itemComments":"","itemTwitterButton":"","itemFacebookButton":"","itemGooglePlusOneButton":"","itemAuthorBlock":"","itemAuthorImage":"","itemAuthorDescription":"","itemAuthorURL":"","itemAuthorEmail":"","itemAuthorLatest":"","itemAuthorLatestLimit":"","itemRelated":"","itemRelatedLimit":"","itemRelatedTitle":"","itemRelatedCategory":"","itemRelatedImageSize":"","itemRelatedIntrotext":"","itemRelatedFulltext":"","itemRelatedAuthor":"","itemRelatedMedia":"","itemRelatedImageGallery":"","itemK2Plugins":""}', '', 'robots=\nauthor=', '', '', 'de-DE'),
(170, 'Corporate social responsibility', 'eke-en', 32, 1, '<p style="text-align: justify;">Respect in humanity, in values, in will, in creativity and equity is a basic concern of CHITOS S.A</p>\r\n', '\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Years ago, in early 2000, the Company chose to integrate into its strategy a new philosophy, solidarity towards people in real need. This conscious corporate decision was evolved and through ZAGORI was substantiated into work and offer! The result nowadays for CHITOS SA is, as an active member of the society, to actively participate in the development and progress of the country, leaving its precious social footprint.</p>\r\n<p>Official bodies and famous NGOs being its companions and collaborators, “ZAGORI” offers and actively supports children, parents, the family, the human, the society throughout Greece and abroad.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Under this philosophy, CHITOS SA has decided to contribute to the establishment of an optimistic attitude, urging people to rethink in this way, proposing to people to recognize the good that has within and to see all small miracles happened around him.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><img src="images/rafahl1.jpg" alt="tokalomesamas" width="600" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Expressing<strong> “the good that we have within”</strong>, we can do everything, as the protagonist of the campaign, Raphael. A restless spirit, a dashing personality, with stubbornness and momentum as each of his age, student at the ELEPAP School and a freshman student at the Faculty of Philosophy, he managed to "fly" with eagle, even though onto the earth he moves only through a wheelchair. But he has “good within”, he feels good and lives every moment in his life “like a miracle”.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">This optimistic message, turned into a scenario, is culminates into social contribution by CHITOS SA in the important work of ELEPAP. The Company "adopted" the ELEPAP needy children throughout Greece, by covering exclusively their programme of rehabilitation! Fulfilling an important need for our little and young friends, who will be able to become useful and active members of our society.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">The message of optimism of the campaign and the social action came to sign the Albert Einstein’s saying: “There are only two ways to live your life. One is as though nothing is a miracle. The other is as though everything is a miracle”.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><img src="images/ekesmall.jpg" alt="ekesmall" width="600" height="128" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>“In Kenya they are thirsty”</strong>: In 2007 CHITOS S.A. in cooperation with ActionAid, has implemented an integrated program of water supply to the region of Giosigkou of Kenya. With this initiative “ZAGORI” water has ensured clean drinking water to 43.000 people, who were suffering from its shortage. The achievement of the project has facilitated the children, in order to go to school without being necessary to cover decades of kilometers for some water. The outbreaks of epidemics due to the lack of clean water were reduced to a great extent, while the women of the region were “nominated” responsible for the management and the viability of the project, acquiring at the same time a particularly important role.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><img src="images/paidia_iroes.jpg" alt="paidia iroes" width="600" height="150" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>“Some children are heroes”</strong>: Immediately after, in 2009, “ZAGORI” water has undertaken a separate initiative for the children and the family. Together with the “Hamogelo tou Paidiou” (Organisation for the protection of children’s rights around the world) has proceeded to the staffing of the Line for the children – SOS 1056, with 9 social workers and 5 psychologists. The experienced staff of the National Line, by answering to more than 330.000 calls, has offered practical aid, by solving problems faced by the parents in relation with their children and the children themselves.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">By investing to this useful tool CHITOS S.A. has managed to stand by to even more children, but also adults, by hoping that actions of such kind can motivate others who would like to offer.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><img src="images/fastrackids.jpg" alt="fastrac kids" width="600" height="123" /></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">At the same time, CHITOS S.A. has participated actively to the voluntary program of enriched education <strong>“FastTracKids for the Non – Privileged Children”</strong>, via which “Zagori water stood by the Protagonists of Tomorrow”: “ZAGORI” has undertaken the transportation of children, - who do not have the financial or social ability- aged from 3 up to 10 years old to the areas of their education.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">It was an initiative via which CHITOS S.A. has sent the message that the creation of opportunities for all the children is not only social requirement but also our duty.</p>', NULL, NULL, '[]', '', '2016-11-28 16:02:29', 191, '', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2016-11-28 16:11:55', 191, '2016-11-22 14:32:57', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 1, 1, 0, 0, '', '', '', '', 4, '{"catItemTitle":"","catItemTitleLinked":"","catItemFeaturedNotice":"","catItemAuthor":"","catItemDateCreated":"","catItemRating":"","catItemImage":"","catItemIntroText":"","catItemExtraFields":"","catItemHits":"","catItemCategory":"","catItemTags":"","catItemAttachments":"","catItemAttachmentsCounter":"","catItemVideo":"","catItemVideoWidth":"","catItemVideoHeight":"","catItemAudioWidth":"","catItemAudioHeight":"","catItemVideoAutoPlay":"","catItemImageGallery":"","catItemImageGalleryWidth":"","catItemImageGalleryHeight":"","catItemDateModified":"","catItemReadMore":"","catItemCommentsAnchor":"","catItemK2Plugins":"","itemDateCreated":"","itemTitle":"","item